This repository contains Brian Gladman's SHA1 & SHA2 code, (the latest release is from 7th January 2007):

  http://gladman.plushost.co.uk/oldsite/cryptography_technology/sha/index.php

Android support has been added by Michael Mohr; simpy clone this repository into your JNI folder and add 'sha' to your modules list.
Further documentation can be found at the top of each source file and in the headers.
